Thanks again Bob…

Ok so anybody searching through here in the future (including myself)…

Use this endpoint to see all your custom label  ids (user_defined) (GET)
<https://api.hubapi.com/crm/v4/associations/deals/contact/labels>

Then use this end point to create association from deal to multiple contacts (POST)
<https://api.hubapi.com/crm/v4/associations/deals/contacts/batch/create>

Example JSON Bellow constructed with ids from the labels endpoint.

{
  “inputs”: [
    {
      “types”: [
        {
          “associationCategory”: “USER_DEFINED”,
          “associationTypeId”: 9
        }
      ],
      “from”: {
        “id”: “15735732607"
      },
      “to”: {
        “id”: “20705051”
      }
    },
    {
      “types”: [
        {
          “associationCategory”: “USER_DEFINED”,
          “associationTypeId”: 7
        }
      ],
      “from”: {
        “id”: “15735732607"
      },
      “to”: {
        “id”: “20710951”
      }
    }
  ]
}
